cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.RO, cs.CV. 

This paper is about improving the efficiency of reinforcement learning algorithms, specifically Deep Q-Networks (DQN), by prioritizing experience replay. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which includes topics such as reinforcement learning and deep learning. The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), robotics (cs.RO), and computer vision (cs.CV), as these are all related fields to machine learning and can be applied to the Atari games used in the experiments.
